solution, and beta,

00:37:18.000 --> 00:37:22.000
which is the designation for the
sodium chloride rich solid solution.

00:37:22.000 --> 00:37:26.000
And how do we figure out the
relative amounts of alpha and beta?

00:37:26.000 --> 00:37:30.000
Lever rule. It is a two phase
regime. Lever rule.

